     H            Y.
     F** VEPR40 ********************************************
     F*  MOVE AB#EP40S TO BACKUP/AB#EP40B BY CREATE DATE   *
     F*  HFILE1/AB#EP40S --> BACKUP/AB#EP40B               *
     F*  J-WATANABE          2018.09.26                    *
     F******************************************************
     FAB#EL40SUF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#EP40BO   E           K        DISK
     F            AB#E40B1                          KRENAMEAB#E40SX
      ***************************************************
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PDATE   8
      *
     C                     MOVE PDATE     XDATE   80
     C           *LOVAL    SETLLAB#EL40S
      * LOOP
     C           *IN90     DOWEQ*OFF
     C                     READ AB#EL40S                 90
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *OFF
      *
     C           ECRDT     IFLE XDATE
     C                     WRITEAB#E40SX
     C                     DELETAB#E40S1
     C                     ELSE
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
